OL,3,C'Labour lacks coherent plan' says Tony
OL,4,CBlair in essay on government failings
OL,6,FFormer prime minister Tony Blair has
OL,7,Fwarned Labour against forcing out Keir
OL,8,FStarmer without having a proper policy
OL,9,Fagenda to follow him, as he launched a
OL,10,Fcriticism of the government's time in
OL,11,Foffice.
OL,13,FBlair, who is the only Labour leader
OL,14,Fto win three general elections, argued
OL,15,Fthe government needs a "fundamental
OL,16,Freset" less than two years after it
OL,17,Fwon the election.
OL,26,@wD@XOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
