OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779894668
OL,3,C'Labour lacks coherent plan' says Tony
OL,4,CBlair in essay on government failings
OL,6,FIn it, he emphasised the impact of AI
OL,7,Fon society, and urged action to be
OL,8,Ftaken on it.
OL,10,FHe said: "Without an agenda of this
OL,11,Fnature, radical but sensible, Britain
OL,12,Fwill continue its long slide towards
OL,13,Frelegation from the Premier League of
OL,14,Fnations."
OL,16,FIt comes as campaigning in Makerfield
OL,17,Fcontinues, with Andy Burnham hopeful
OL,18,Fof holding the seat for Labour in the
OL,19,Fby-election on June 18.
OL,26,@rD@JOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
