OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1779894668
OL,3,C'Labour lacks coherent plan' says Tony
OL,4,CBlair in essay on government failings
OL,6,FBurnham is expected to challenge
OL,7,FStarmer for the leadership if he wins
OL,8,Fthe seat on the outskirts of Wigan,
OL,9,Ffor which Labour is defending a 5,399
OL,10,Fmajority.
OL,12,FBlair praised both Burnham and Wes
OL,13,FStreeting ` another potential
OL,14,Fleadership challenger ` in his essay.
OL,16,FWhile he praised investment in
OL,17,Finfrastructure, planning reforms and
OL,18,Fimmigration policies, Blair detailed
OL,19,Fdeeper shortcomings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
