OL,3,C'Labour lacks coherent plan' says Tony
OL,4,CBlair in essay on government failings
OL,6,FThe Workers Rights Bill, an
OL,7,F"acceleration of net-zero", and
OL,8,Fphasing out of British oil and gas
OL,9,Fcame under particular fire from the
OL,10,Fformer prime minister.
